            "title": "盤中速報 - 雙鍵(4764)股價拉至漲停，漲停價170.5元，成交4,559張",
            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>雙鍵(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:4764:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/4764\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">4764-TW</a>)13日10:27上漲15.5元，股價漲停報170.5元，委買631張，成交4,559張。</p></section><p></p><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>主要業務為塑膠添加劑及UV光固化產品等產品之研發、製造與銷售。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>雙鍵(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:4764:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/4764\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">4764-TW</a>)近5日股價上漲28.1%，集中市場<a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/TWS/TSE01\">加權指數</a>上漲8.74%，股價漲幅表現優於大盤。</p></section><section><p><em>近5日籌碼</em></p></section><section style=\"margin-top:20px\"><ul> <li>三大法人合計買賣超：+1,136 張</li> <li>外資買賣超：+777 張</li> <li>投信買賣超：-4 張</li> <li>自營商買賣超：+363 張</li> <li>融資增減：-113 張</li> <li>融券增減：+22 張</li> </ul></section></main>",
